    {
      "para_id": "Q001964.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Inana of Mur , her Inana , Lamassatum , ( Lipit-Estar's ) mother built the E-maruru , her beloved storehouse in Isin for the well-being of Lipit-Eštar , the shepherd who heeds the gods , king of Sumer and Akkad , spouse of Inana , and also for her ( own ) well-being ."
    }
  ],
